snippet.title: Crimsonland Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Ultra-gratifying top-down hardcore dual stick shooter Crimsonland is now available for Windows, OS X, Linux, Playstation 4, Playstation 3, Playstation Vita and iOS!

Check out full availability and download links at http://www.10tons.com/Game/crimsonland_rm.html
